name: BestFantasyTeamNames.com
tag_list: fantasy-sports, fantasy-football, fantasy-baseball, fantasy-basketball, fantasy-hockey, fantasy-golf
overview: What’s in a fantasy team name? EVERYTHING! The name you choose is your team’s identity, it’s soul, it’s karma, if you will. At BestFantasyTeamNames.com, they consider themselves the Library of Congress when it comes to fantasy sports team names. Their databases have been described as cool, hilarious, awesome, dirty, offensive, funny, stupid, and juvenile. Some are rude, some are clever; some involve current events and pop culture (see John Clayton’s Ponytail). Users can submit new fantasy team names which are added to the database and can be voted up in the overall rankings.
